      src: "https://leetcode.cn/circle/discuss/mOr1u6/",
      summary:
        ":::example 模板來源 https://leetcode.cn/circle/discuss/m_or…\n模板：\n\n```cpp\n// 模板來源 https://leetcode.cn/circle/discuss/m_or1u6/\nstruct UnionFind {\n  vector<int> fa, sz;\n  int cc;\n  explicit UnionFind(int n) : fa(n), sz(n, 1), cc(n) {\n    iota(fa.begin(), fa.end(), 0);\n  }\n\n  int find(int x) {\n    if (fa[x] != x) {\n      fa[x] = find(fa[x]);  // 路徑壓縮\n    }\n    return fa[x];\n  }\n\n  bool isSame(int x, int y) { return find(x) == find(y); }\n\n  bool merge(int x, int y) {\n    x = find(x);\n    y = find(y);\n    if (x == y) {\n      return false;\n    }\n    fa[x] = y;  // 小的掛到大的下面（啟發式合併）\n    sz[y] += sz[x];\n    cc -= 1;\n    return true;\n  }\n\n  int getSize(int x) { return sz[find(x)]; }\n};\n```\n:::",
